  <item nodeId="node-179">
    <command xml:space="preserve">open purple</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">As you open the purple capsa, an almost-palpable wave of force emanates from it, as the power of the revealed scroll of rezrov is released.&#x000A;Another Important Door clicks as it unlocks!&#x000A;Another Important Door flies open!&#x000A;The straps and buckles on your rucksack fly open and it falls!&#x000A;&#x000A;Dropped.&#x000A;&#x000A;Also, you alert everyone to your presence, and they start heading straight for you.  Fortunately, they are, as of yet, unimplemented.  LS DEBUG.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
    <children>
      <child nodeId="node-180"/>
    </children>
  </item>
